h2.text-xl.font-bold.mb-4 #{station.name}駅に到着🎉

= image_tag station_image_path(station:),
            class: 'md:max-w-40 md:max-h-40 max-h-32 max-w-32 mx-auto',
            width: "200", height: "200",
            alt: "#{station.name}駅のイラスト"

p.mt-2
  | 歩いた駅は#{number_of_walked}駅（残り#{number_of_remaining}駅）、
  br
  | 歩いた距離は約#{arrived_distance}kmです！
